OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FWednesday morning will be dry
OL,6,Fand bright. Increasing cloud bringing
OL,7,Foutbreaks of rain later in the
OL,8,Fafternoon with a freshening wind. Much
OL,9,Fof the rain is likely across the Dales
OL,10,Fand Pennines. Some eastern parts
OL,11,Fprobably remaining dry and warm.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA cloudy evening and night
OL,14,Fwith outbreaks of rain affecting much
OL,15,Fof the region. Some heavy bursts are
OL,16,Flikely across the Pennines. Drier
OL,17,Flater in the night. Gusty winds
OL,18,Fthroughout.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
