OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FThursday remaining mostly
OL,6,Fdry and breezy, with some clear or
OL,7,Fsunny spells. Temperatures close to
OL,8,Faverage.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FFriday
OL,11,Fand into the weekend likely to remain
OL,12,Fdry and breezy, with some clear or
OL,13,Fsunny spells. Light rain possible
OL,14,Facross Pennines. Temperatures close to
OL,15,For slightly above average throughout.
